item.title: Working with R and Python
item.description: Looking at Earthquake Data Near Fiji using R and Python Fun Fact: I visited Fiji when I was 4 and have been dying to go back ever since! I have extended family who lives there and an aunt who grew up there when she was young after moving from India. All of the pictures I have from this trip are on old film or physically printed, so here's a picture of this beautiful country that I found online.
